                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000468b0dd5-0649-4f9c-a4b0-414b06c3e0a0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\({F}^{{'}}=c\frac{{\left({q}^{{'}}\right)}^{2}}{{\left({r}^{{'}}\right)}^{2}}=c\frac{{\left(\frac{q}{2}\right)}^{2}}{{\left(2r\right)}^{2}}\ ⇒{F}^{{'}}=\frac{c{q}^{2}}{{r}^{2}}\times \frac{1}{4\times 4}⇒{F}^{{'}}=\frac{F}{16}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001468b0dd5-0649-4f9c-a4b0-414b06c3e0a0"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000468b0dd5-0649-4f9c-a4b0-414b06c3e0a0 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001468b0dd5-0649-4f9c-a4b0-414b06c3e0a0 {font-family: SolaimanLipi;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
