                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000778707e0-e18d-4339-81a9-ca3acecce480" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001778707e0-e18d-4339-81a9-ca3acecce480">awi</span><span class="pt-000001778707e0-e18d-4339-81a9-ca3acecce480">,</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000002778707e0-e18d-4339-81a9-ca3acecce480"> </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(y=2{x}^{2}-x+2⇒\frac{dy}{dx}=4x-1=0\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000003778707e0-e18d-4339-81a9-ca3acecce480"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000778707e0-e18d-4339-81a9-ca3acecce480 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001778707e0-e18d-4339-81a9-ca3acecce480 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-000002778707e0-e18d-4339-81a9-ca3acecce480 {font-family: ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-000003778707e0-e18d-4339-81a9-ca3acecce480 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000091f11a2d-df29-492a-b8e1-87b05dc99a67" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∴x=\frac{1}{4}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000191f11a2d-df29-492a-b8e1-87b05dc99a67"> ; </span><a id="_Hlk166764571" class="pt-00000291f11a2d-df29-492a-b8e1-87b05dc99a67"></a><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\frac{{d}^{2}y}{d{x}^{2}}=4&gt;0;y=2\times \frac{1}{{4}^{2}}-\frac{1}{4}+2=\frac{15}{8}\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000091f11a2d-df29-492a-b8e1-87b05dc99a67 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000191f11a2d-df29-492a-b8e1-87b05dc99a67 {font-family: SolaimanLipi;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}a.pt-00000291f11a2d-df29-492a-b8e1-87b05dc99a67 {text-decoration: none;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000098eb7f00-31c9-4e81-b0cd-ff8282919e64" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><a id="_Hlk167616279" class="pt-00000198eb7f00-31c9-4e81-b0cd-ff8282919e64"></a><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000298eb7f00-31c9-4e81-b0cd-ff8282919e64">Shortcut: </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\({y}_{min}=c-\frac{{b}^{2}}{4a}=2-\frac{{\left(-1\right)}^{2}}{4\times 2}=\frac{15}{8}\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000098eb7f00-31c9-4e81-b0cd-ff8282919e64 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}a.pt-00000198eb7f00-31c9-4e81-b0cd-ff8282919e64 {text-decoration: none;}span.pt-00000298eb7f00-31c9-4e81-b0cd-ff8282919e64 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
