                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-00000039531cb7-638b-4c2f-9342-21d91e471ac4" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(y=x+\frac{1}{x}\ ;\ \ {y}_{1}=1-\frac{1}{{x}^{2}}\ ;\ \ {y}_{2}=\frac{2}{{x}^{3}}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000139531cb7-638b-4c2f-9342-21d91e471ac4"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000039531cb7-638b-4c2f-9342-21d91e471ac4 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000139531cb7-638b-4c2f-9342-21d91e471ac4 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000000ef85878-fdfa-4685-833a-59b26867c834" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-0000010ef85878-fdfa-4685-833a-59b26867c834">Myi&#230;gvb</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000010ef85878-fdfa-4685-833a-59b26867c834"> </span><span class="pt-0000010ef85878-fdfa-4685-833a-59b26867c834">ev</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000010ef85878-fdfa-4685-833a-59b26867c834"> </span><span class="pt-0000010ef85878-fdfa-4685-833a-59b26867c834">jNy</span><span class="pt-0000010ef85878-fdfa-4685-833a-59b26867c834">gv</span><span class="pt-0000010ef85878-fdfa-4685-833a-59b26867c834">‡</span><span class="pt-0000010ef85878-fdfa-4685-833a-59b26867c834">bi</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000010ef85878-fdfa-4685-833a-59b26867c834"> Rb&#168;</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000020ef85878-fdfa-4685-833a-59b26867c834"> </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\({y}_{1}=0⇒1-\frac{1}{{x}^{2}}=0∴x=±1\ ;\ \) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000020ef85878-fdfa-4685-833a-59b26867c834"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000000ef85878-fdfa-4685-833a-59b26867c834 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000010ef85878-fdfa-4685-833a-59b26867c834 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-0000020ef85878-fdfa-4685-833a-59b26867c834 {font-family: SolaimanLipi;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000c90df193-4e1e-40a0-9338-b488f6a8c363" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(x=1\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001c90df193-4e1e-40a0-9338-b488f6a8c363"> n‡j, </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\({y}_{2}=\frac{2}{1}=2&gt;0\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000002c90df193-4e1e-40a0-9338-b488f6a8c363"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000c90df193-4e1e-40a0-9338-b488f6a8c363 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001c90df193-4e1e-40a0-9338-b488f6a8c363 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-000002c90df193-4e1e-40a0-9338-b488f6a8c363 {font-family: SolaimanLipi;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000002face42f-e02c-414f-a47b-232edc595325" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∴x=1\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000012face42f-e02c-414f-a47b-232edc595325"> </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000022face42f-e02c-414f-a47b-232edc595325">Gi Rb&#168; </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(y=x+\frac{1}{x}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000012face42f-e02c-414f-a47b-232edc595325"> </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000022face42f-e02c-414f-a47b-232edc595325">Gi </span><span class="pt-0000022face42f-e02c-414f-a47b-232edc595325">jNygvb</span><span xml:sp