                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000cc81fede-ca5e-4f56-b408-3bf4ae4a034c" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\frac{0}{0}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001cc81fede-ca5e-4f56-b408-3bf4ae4a034c"> </span><span class="pt-000002cc81fede-ca5e-4f56-b408-3bf4ae4a034c">AvKv‡ii</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000002cc81fede-ca5e-4f56-b408-3bf4ae4a034c"> </span><span class="pt-000002cc81fede-ca5e-4f56-b408-3bf4ae4a034c">e‡j</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000002cc81fede-ca5e-4f56-b408-3bf4ae4a034c"> </span><span class="pt-000003cc81fede-ca5e-4f56-b408-3bf4ae4a034c">L’Hopital</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000002cc81fede-ca5e-4f56-b408-3bf4ae4a034c"> Gi </span><span class="pt-000002cc81fede-ca5e-4f56-b408-3bf4ae4a034c">wbqg</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000002cc81fede-ca5e-4f56-b408-3bf4ae4a034c"> Abyhvqx, </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000cc81fede-ca5e-4f56-b408-3bf4ae4a034c {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001cc81fede-ca5e-4f56-b408-3bf4ae4a034c {font-family: Arial;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-000002cc81fede-ca5e-4f56-b408-3bf4ae4a034c {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-000003cc81fede-ca5e-4f56-b408-3bf4ae4a034c {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000000c788945-efa9-4bc7-bb3a-2d6beb015e3d" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\underset{x→0}{lim}\frac{\frac{d}{dx}\ \left({e}^{x}-{e}^{-x}-2ln\ {\left(1+x\right)}\right)}{\frac{d}{dx}\ \left(xsin\ {x}\right)}=\underset{x→0}{lim}\frac{{e}^{x}+{e}^{-x}-\frac{2}{1+x}}{sin\ {x}+xcos\ {x}}\) </s