                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br />
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000292999f3-3269-4956-aa2e-e0459d86b15a" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(y={log}_{y}\ {x}⇒x={y}^{y}⇒ln\ {x}=yln\ {y}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001292999f3-3269-4956-aa2e-e0459d86b15a"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000292999f3-3269-4956-aa2e-e0459d86b15a {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001292999f3-3269-4956-aa2e-e0459d86b15a {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000006a7aa705-53d5-476c-a082-5d6adea89a58" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒\frac{1}{x}=y\times \frac{1}{y}\times \frac{dy}{dx}+(ln\ {y})\times \frac{dy}{dx}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000016a7aa705-53d5-476c-a082-5d6adea89a58"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000006a7aa705-53d5-476c-a082-5d6adea89a58 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000016a7aa705-53d5-476c-a082-5d6adea89a58 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000500d1d39-a090-4029-8d46-cdf958498519" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒\frac{1}{x}=\frac{dy}{dx}\left(1+ln\ {y}\right)∴\frac{dy}{dx}=\frac{1}{x\left(1+ln\ {y}\right)}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001500d1d39-a090-4029-8d46-cdf958498519"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000500d1d39-a090-4029-8d46-cdf958498519 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001500d1d39-a090-4029-8d46-cdf958498519 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
